SyncState *

############################# binarin@gmail.com
IMAPAccount binarin@gmail.com
Host imap.gmail.com
User binarin@gmail.com
PassCmd "cat ~/.rc.d/10-desktop-secrets/binarin@gmail.com"
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore binarin@gmail.com-remote
Account binarin@gmail.com

MaildirStore binarin@gmail.com-local
Path ~/.mail/binarin@gmail.com/
Inbox ~/.mail/binarin@gmail.com/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

MaildirStore binarin@gmail.com-archive
Path ~/.mail/archive-binarin@gmail.com/

Channel binarin@gmail.com-archive
Master ":binarin@gmail.com-remote:[Gmail]/All Mail"
Slave ":binarin@gmail.com-archive:Archive"
Create Slave
SyncState *
Sync Push Flags

Channel binarin@gmail.com-trash
Master ":binarin@gmail.com-remote:[Gmail]/Trash"
Slave ":binarin@gmail.com-archive:Trash"
Create Slave
Sync All

Channel binarin@gmail.com-drafts
Master ":binarin@gmail.com-remote:[Gmail]/Drafts"
Slave ":binarin@gmail.com-local:Drafts"
Create Slave
Sync All
Expunge Both

Channel binarin@gmail.com-sent
Master ":binarin@gmail.com-remote:[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Slave ":binarin@gmail.com-local:Sent"
Create Slave
Sync All
Expunge Both

Channel binarin@gmail.com-inbox
Master ":binarin@gmail.com-remote:INBOX"
Slave ":binarin@gmail.com-local:INBOX"
Create Slave
Sync All
Expunge Both

Channel binarin@gmail.com-user-labels
Master :binarin@gmail.com-remote:
Slave :binarin@gmail.com-local:
Create Slave
Sync All
Patterns "*" "!Drafts" "!Sent" "!Trash" "![Gmail]*" "!INBOX" "!Lists*" "!Cron*"
Expunge Both

Channel binarin@gmail.com-mailing-lists-and-notifications
Master :binarin@gmail.com-remote:
Slave :binarin@gmail.com-local:
Create Slave
Sync All
Patterns "Lists*" "Cron*"
MaxMessages 2000
Expunge Both

Group binarin@gmail.com
Channel binarin@gmail.com-trash
Channel binarin@gmail.com-inbox
Channel binarin@gmail.com-drafts
Channel binarin@gmail.com-sent
Channel binarin@gmail.com-user-labels
Channel binarin@gmail.com-mailing-lists-and-notifications
Channel binarin@gmail.com-archive

